Participation

The dataset we analyzed on 2019-09-05 has 300 rows and 26 variables. We have data from 3 sites: Boston, Denver and Seattle. The number of participants per site is as follows:


Boston has 100 participants
Denver has 100 participants
Seattle has 100 participants

We have data from 3 arms: F: FOLFOX, G: IROX and A: IFL. The number of participants per arm is as follows:
